verses.text:
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
There our hearts shall rest forever, By and by.

We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
With our loved ones gone before us, By and by.

We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
And the storms of life are over, By and by.

We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
We shall meet beyond the river, By and by, by and by;
Where the light of love is streaming, By and by.
